---
title: "US52 — Profile verified by admin"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ExpertProfileScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>WatchVerificationStatus
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ExpertProfile · ExpertVerificationDocument
  note over A: expert submitted credentials (US41) — admin reviews them (US57)
  A->>B: open profile / verification banner
  B->>C: watchStatus(expertId)
  C->>E: fetchExpertProfile(expertId)
  alt admin approved
    E-->>C: ExpertProfile (status = verified)
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (verified)
    B-->>A: VERIFIED badge shown, listings go live
  else admin rejected
    E-->>C: ExpertProfile (status = rejected, reason)
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (rejected)
    B-->>A: rejection reason + resubmit credentials
  end
  note over E: fetchExpertProfile via SupabaseGateway → expert_profiles (RLS).<br/>status set by admin in ReviewExpertVerification (US57)
